@Node FAQ "OLGA: F.A.Q "

@{B} F . A . Q . @{UB}

__________________________________________________________________________
@{FG SHINE}ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{FG TEXT}


@{B}Is Olga handling Olitec Speed Voice modem ?@{UB}

Olga uses the Self Memory modem functions. Some functions can be used with
voice modem (Speed Voice) but the importants functions will bring the modem
to communication breaks.

It is possible to know the modem type by using the terminal emulator and typing
the commande AT/. The modem answers the manufacturer reference.


@{B}Is Olga handling Fax ?@{UB} 

No. Olga only downloads Fax into files on the harddrives (*.Fax).

Howerver, It is possible the send back a Fax strored in the memory modem to an
other Fax (See part @{"remote fax download" link FReg})

Fax handling will be developped in a next Olga release.



@{B}What is the Voice file format (*.voc) ?@{UB}

The files are in ADPCM4 format. In the current release, it is not possible
to play the messages with the Amiga's speaker.

We plan to develop a player function first and, is we've enough time, 
a IFF/ADPCM4 converter function.


@{B}The record quality of the greatings message is not very good. What
to do ?@{UB}

The quality of the integreted 33600 version micro gives average results when
recording. It's better to use the external micro (available in some versions)
  

It is possible to use the telephone by following the guide provided by
the software and the doc. The quality is quite good but the record duration
is limited to about 15 seconds.


@{B}Recording a greating message by using a telephone is impossible. Why ?@{UB}

The modem and the telephone must be connected on different connector. Don't
connect the telephone on the modem line connector. (see part @{"Record a 
greetings message" link FAcc}



@{B}The Olga windows doesn't open at launch@{UB}

It is possible that the window doesn't open at all if the resolution is
to low. In this case, try higher resolution or overscan (could be suffisant).


__________________________________________________________________________
@{FG SHINE}ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ@{FG TEXT}

@Endnode

